#. type: Title ===
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/datasource.adoc:526
#, no-wrap
msgid "Named Datasources"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/datasource.adoc:531
msgid "When using Dev Services the default datasource will always be created, but to specify a named datasource you need to have at least one build time property so Quarkus knows to create the datasource. In general you will usually either specify the `db-kind` property, or explicitly enable DevDb: `quarkus.datasource.\"name\".devservices.enabled=true`."
